{"notes_translated": {"fr": "La «banque de données de levés géochimiques du Canada» a deux objectifs à long terme. Premièrement, cette banque de données vise à constituer un inventaire de tous les levés géochimiques régionaux qui ont été effectués au Canada, à partir des années 50. Deuxièmement, elle vise à rendre accessible dans un format standard, les données brutes de ces levés. Plus de 1300 levés ont été répertoriés. De ceux-ci, les données brutes de plus de 150 ont été converties en format standard.", "en": "The \"Canadian Database of Geochemical Surveys\" has two long-term goals. Firstly, it aims to catalogue all of the regional geochemical surveys that have been carried out across Canada, beginning in the 1950s. Secondly, it aims to make the raw data from those surveys available in a standardised format. Over 1,300 surveys have been catalogued. Of these, the raw data for over 150 have been converted to a standardised format."}, "imso_approval": "true", "creator": "Stephen Adcock", "locale": "fra", "jurisdiction": "federal", "maintainer_email": "nrcan.gsc-geosciencedata-donneesgeoscience-cgc.rncan@canada.ca", "position_name": {"fr": "", "en": ""}, "frequency": "continual", "keywords": {"fr": ["Hydrogéologie"], "en": ["Hydrogeology"]}, "ready_to_publish": "true", "id": "b174e9f5-e8ea-f99a-9bc9-f8162650c024", "subject": ["form_descriptors", "science_and_technology", "nature_and_environment"], "spatial_representation_type": ["text_table"], "distributor": "{\"fr\": {\"city\": \"Ottawa\", \"administrative_area\": \"Ontario\", \"country\": \"Canada\", \"organization_name\": \"Gouvernement du Canada; Ressources naturelles Canada; Commission g\\u00e9ologique du Canada - CGC Centre du Canada\", \"postal_code\": \"\", \"address\": \"601 Booth Street\", \"electronic_mail_address\": \"stephenw.adcock@canada.ca\"}, \"en\": {\"city\": \"Ottawa\", \"administrative_area\": \"Ontario\", \"country\": \"Canada\", \"organization_name\": \"Government of Canada; Natural Resources Canada; Geological Survey of Canada - GSC Central Canada\", \"postal_code\": \"\", \"address\": \"601 Booth Street\", \"electronic_mail_address\": \"stephenw.adcock@canada.ca\"}}", "contact_information": "{\"fr\": {\"electronic_mail_address\": \"nrcan.gsc-geosciencedata-donneesgeoscience-cgc.rncan@canada.ca\"}, \"en\": {\"electronic_mail_address\": \"nrcan.gsc-geosciencedata-donneesgeoscience-cgc.rncan@canada.ca\"}}", "state": "active", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\",\"coordinates\": [[[-144.0,41.0],[-52.0,41.0],[-52.0,84.0],[-144.0,84.0],[-144.0,41.0]]]}", "time_period_coverage_start": "2016-01-17", "title_translated": {"fr": "Banque de données de levés géochimiques du Canada", "en": "Canadian Database of Geochemical Surveys"}, "type": "dataset", "resources": [{"url": "https://geochem.nrcan.gc.ca/cgi-bin/GSC_Geochemistry/wms?service=WMS&request=GetCapabilities&version=1.3.0&layers=GSC_EN_Geochemical_Surveys&legend_format=image/png&feature_info_type=text/html", "name_translated": {"fr": "CAN GSC Geochemical Surveys Index - All Surveys (Layer)", "en": "CAN GSC Geochemical Surveys Index - All Surveys (Layer)"}, "language": ["fr"], "resource_type": "web_service", "format": "WMS"}, {"url": "https://geochem.nrcan.gc.ca/cgi-bin/GSC_Geochemistry/wms?service=WMS&request=GetCapabilities&version=1.3.0&layers=GSC_EN_Geochemical_Surveys&legend_format=image/png&feature_info_type=text/html", "name_translated": {"fr": "CAN GSC Geochemical Surveys Index - All Surveys (Layer)", "en": "CAN GSC Geochemical Surveys Index - All Surveys (Layer)"}, "language": ["en"], "resource_type": "web_service", "format": "WMS"}], "status": "ongoing", "source_metadata_date_created": "2018-10-23", "topic_category": ["geoscientific_information"], "restrictions": "unrestricted", "aggregate_identifier": "", "responsible_role": "RI_414,RI_418", "collection": "fgp", "date_published": "2016-01-18", "display_flags": ["fgp_viewer"], "reference_system_information": "EPSG:4326,http://www.epsg-registry.org/,6.